Enum BinaryInteractionType

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<BinaryInteractionType>
      • org.biopax.paxtools.io.sif.BinaryInteractionType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<BinaryInteractionType>

    public enum BinaryInteractionType
extends Enum<BinaryInteractionType>
    This class holds the description, tag (used in SIF file), the information if the interaction is directed for the relevant binary interaction types.
